title: GET_INTERIOR_PORTAL_ROOM_TO
content:
0x3F47F0E8// GetInteriorPortalRoomTo
int GET_INTERIOR_PORTAL_ROOM_TO(int interiorId, int portalIndex);Parameters:interiorId: The target interior.portalIndex: Interior portal index.Returns: Portal's room TO index.Examples:Lualocal playerPed = PlayerPedId()
local interiorId = GetInteriorFromEntity(playerPed)

if interiorId ~= 0 then
  local roomIndex = 0

  local portalRoomTo = GetInteriorPortalRoomTo(interiorId, 0)
  print("portal " .. roomIndex .. " room TO is: " .. portalRoomTo)
end
